data.description: Welcome home! This charming home has 5 spacious bedrooms, ample living space, and a backyard great for entertaining! New LVP has been run throughout, and offering a carpet allowance for the new owners to make it their own! You will not be disappointed with the large kitchen, or the 5th bedroom downstairs that could be used for so many things! Solar Panels installed in 2020, making electric bill almost disappear! Centrally located in the heart of Hampton, this home is a close distance to the beach!  Call today to schedule your private showing!
